✨ HOLIDAY BLOWOUT X AIRWRAP ✨ 
Get the perfect soft holiday blow out with no effort and in a few short minutes. Rotate direction of each curl by twisting the tip, use the largest barrel only for a few seconds on hot and a few on cold (depending on hair type or density). We aren’t going for curls, just a soft blown out look. Finish the look by pulling one side back and up, and adding some beautiful @leletny accessories 
#dysonhair #dysonairwrap #dysonprohair #leletny

✨ HOLIDAY PARTY PONY ✨ 
pull your hair back to a ponytail above your occipital bone. Then take small sections of the pony and curl opposite directions using your @dysonhair CORRALE straightener by rotating it in a 360 motion and slowly pull down the section.  Finish it off with a @leletny ponytail cuff. @dysonhairpro #dysonhair #dysonprohair #leletny #holidayhair #ponytail #dysoncorrale

✨ HOLIDAY UPDO ✨ 
From a ponytail twist the lengths until tight then wrap around the base. Leave 3 inches of the ends out then straighten with your #dysoncorrale flat iron and fan it out. Then add a stunning statement accessory from @leletny. Finally straighten the front money pieces with a slight bend to frame your jawline. @dysonhair @dysonhairpro #dysonhair #dysonhairpro #leletny #holidayhair

✨ THE SCRUNGEE ✨ 
This idea came to me almost 3 years ago. I partnered with @shopchelseaking 2 years ago to develop what you see here. Made with love, and hand made in 🇨🇦. @thescrungee will guaranteed help you “FIND YOUR PERFECT HOLD” no matter the texture or density. Head now to www.thescrungee.Com to get yours. (Shipped globally)  #hairtie #thescrungee #hairhack #ponytail #workouthairstyle

✨ HOW TO USE @thescrungee ✨
1. Get your ponytail in place..high, medium, or low
2. Put first hook in base of pony between your hand and head
3. Keep the scrungee in place with the hand holding your pony
4. Wrap scrungee around pony till your desired tightness 
5. Secure last hook also in the base of the ponytail closest to head
To remove: unhook the last hook you placed and it will unravel 
#thescrungee #hairtips #ponytail

4. Don’t over complicate it
